# gitlab-templates
Description Templates for Gitlab


Add the submodule by running this command from the projects root directory

git submodule add https://github.com/vkhansen/gitlab-templates.git


Place templates in .gitlab/issue_templates/ directory in your repository. (using command above)
Commit and push to your default(typically master) branch.

How it works:
https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/user/project/description_templates.html

More info:
https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/7766



